OL,4,CDisabled girl, 10, in three-year wait
OL,5,Cfor new wheelchair, says dad
OL,6, A severely disabled 10-year-old girl is
OL,7, facing unacceptable delays in securing
OL,8, the right wheelchair for her needs, her
OL,9, family has said.
OL,11,FCharlie Burridge has an NHS chair but
OL,12,Fit does not support her head, which she
OL,13,Fneeds to be able to communicate.
OL,15,FThe family, from North Tyneside, said
OL,16,Fit is taking too long to be seen at
OL,17,FNewcastle's Freeman hospital.
OL,19,FThe hospital said the wait had been
OL,20,F"due to the clinics being booked and
OL,21,Fannual leave issues".
